Subject: [PATCH 3/4] Refactor into a completely Krita native plugin

---
 CMakeLists.txt                             | 33 +++++++++++++++++-----
 src/Host/KritaPlugin/gmicqttoolplugin.cpp  |  9 ++++++
 src/Host/KritaPlugin/gmicqttoolplugin.h    | 15 +++++-----
